    <item>
      <title>Best Budget Build Tools for a First Van Conversion</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/best-of/budget-build-tools/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/best-of/budget-build-tools/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You do not need a garage full of tools for a strong first build. You need a small set of reliable tools and a clear sequence.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;callout-shortcode&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;callout-title&#34;&gt;Quick Answer&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;callout-body&#34;&gt;Buy fewer tools but buy reliable core tools: drill/driver, jigsaw, rivnut tool, crimper, torque wrench, and safety gear.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;comparetable-wrap my-6&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;overflow-x-auto hidden md:block&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;table class=&#34;min-w-full border-collapse text-sm&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Product&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Best For&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Price&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Pros&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Cons&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;CTA&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3 font-semibold&#34;&gt;Drill/Driver Combo Kit&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Nearly every build task&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;$$&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Highest utility per dollar&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Battery ecosystem lock-in&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-neutral-300 bg-transparent text-neutral-500 opacity-70 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-di